body:
Consider the less verbose version:

```c++
return BIP22ValidationResult(dos_state.IsValid() ? sc.state : dos_state);
```

Or use a guard clause to be consistent with the previous `if`:

```c++
if (!dos_state.IsValid()) {
    return BIP22ValidationResult(dos_state);
}

return BIP22ValidationResult(sc.state);
```

