Actually, you can remove the duplicate check on `dos_state.IsValid()` like so:

```c++
if (!dos_state.IsValid()) {
    return BIP22ValidationResult(dos_state);
}

if (!sc.found) {
    return "inconclusive";
}

return BIP22ValidationResult(sc.state);
```

